    "body": "Hmm, I think they are not following the spec correctly in this case. Check the response to the `eth_getTransactionReceipt` method [here](https://ethereum.github.io/execution-apis/api-documentation/).\r\n\r\nI wrote to them let them know about this.\r\n\r\nI'm tentatively closing this issue because we normally try to avoid relaxing validations to accommodate the quirks of RPC providers. But I will re-consider it if they don't fix it quickly enough. Please ping me here if that's the case!",
